This week, stargazers have the chance to witness a six-planet alignment, with Venus, Mars, Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, and Neptune forming a celestial arc in the southern and eastern skies. ü™êü§©

The event peaks in visibility on the nights of January 17 and 18, shortly after sunset. Four of these planets‚ÄîVenus, Mars, Jupiter, and Saturn‚Äîwill be visible to the naked eye, while Uranus and Neptune require a telescope for observation.

Such alignments, while visually stunning, are not as rare as one might think. They occur when planets align in the same sector of the sky due to their orbits around the Sun.

The Biden administration has indicated it will not enforce the nationwide TikTok ban set to take effect on Sunday, leaving the decision to President-elect Donald Trump. üá∫üá∏üì±

While the law targets app stores and hosting services supporting TikTok due to its Chinese ownership, the Biden team says the timing, just one day before the inauguration, shifts the responsibility to the next administration. 

Despite the looming ban, tech companies like Apple and Google have yet to reveal how they will proceed. Meanwhile, Trump has expressed his intent to save the platform, citing its popularity and role in his campaign. 

Reports suggest Trump‚Äôs team is exploring options to delay or negotiate the ban, including a potential executive order. The Supreme Court‚Äôs ruling on the ban and Trump‚Äôs next steps are expected to shape TikTok‚Äôs future in the U.S.

A Rover.com study, The Truth About Dog People, found that 65% of dog owners take more photos of their pets than their significant others.

The survey of thousands revealed that 54% would consider ending a relationship if their dog disliked their partner. 

47% find it harder to leave their dog than their partner, and 56% greet their dog first when arriving home.

David Lynch, the visionary filmmaker renowned for works like ‚ÄúTwin Peaks,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Velvet,‚Äù and ‚ÄúMulholland Drive,‚Äù has passed away at the age of 78. 

His family announced his death on January 16, 2025.  Lynch‚Äôs distinctive ‚ÄúLynchian‚Äù style, marked by surreal and dreamlike elements, significantly influenced modern cinema. In August 2024, he revealed he had been diagnosed with emphysema, attributed to his years of smoking. 

Beyond filmmaking, Lynch was also a painter, musician, and advocate for Transcendental Meditation. He is survived by his four children from previous marriages.
